    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hey @francovilla could you try upgrading to the latest Truffle v5.1.67? We just made some rather significant performance improvements to the Truffle bundle, and I'm hopeful that this sort of memory problem will now not be a problem.\r\n\r\nIf that isn't the case, you can always try giving Node.js more memory, e.g. (instead of `truffle migrate`):\r\n```console\r\n$ node `which truffle` --max-old-space-size=8192 migrate\r\n```\r\n\r\nPlease let us know! Sorry about this.",
